    content: "Fragrance is a rare dropshipping niche: customers search for exact branded products (\"Chanel No 5 EDP 3.4oz\"), prices are comparable, and repeat purchase rates are high. We run a live fragrance dropshipping store \u2014 here is the full setup.\n\n## Why fragrance works for dropshipping\n\nUnlike gadget dropshipping, fragrance demand is brand-driven and evergreen. Nobody needs to be convinced they want Versace Eros \u2014 they are comparing prices. That changes your job from persuasion to **merchandising, trust, and search visibility**.\n\n## Supplier options\n\nThe dominant US wholesale suppliers for fragrance dropshipping offer 9,000\u201320,000 SKU catalogs across fragrance, skincare, haircare, and makeup with 200+ brands. Evaluate: dropship program fees, live stock feeds, MAP restrictions, and shipping times to your market. A supplier with daily CSV/API inventory exports is essential \u2014 perfume stock moves fast and selling out-of-stock items destroys trust.\n\n## Store setup essentials\n\n- **Navigation built on the real catalog**: organize by Fragrance, Skincare, Haircare, Bath & Body, Makeup, and Brands \u2014 matching how buyers browse\n- **Variant structure**: same scent, multiple sizes (1oz / 1.7oz / 3.4oz) must share one product with size variants, not duplicate listings\n- **Image quality**: supplier images are often 500\u00d7500px; request high-resolution feeds or source brand imagery, and never let your theme upscale small images\n- **Boutique product descriptions**: rewrite supplier copy in prose with fragrance notes (top, heart, base) \u2014 this is both a conversion and an SEO play\n\n## Margins and pricing\n\nExpect 15\u201330% gross margins after supplier and dropship fees. Winning strategies: bundle gift sets, target long-tail size-specific searches, and run abandoned-cart email flows (fragrance carts recover unusually well because intent is high).\n\n## SEO for fragrance stores\n\nCollection page descriptions, brand pages, and product schema are your growth levers. Target \"brand + product + size\" queries where competition is thin and intent is maximal.\n\n---\n\n**Need help implementing this?** eCeez builds and optimizes Shopify stores for DTC brands. [Explore our Shopify SEO services](/seo) or [get a store built in days](/shopify-store-setup-service).",
