    id: "shopify-for-fragrance-brands",
    title: "Shopify for Fragrance Brands: Store Setup, UX & SEO That Sells Scent Online",
    subtitle: "Selling scent online means selling imagery, notes, and trust. Here's the blueprint.",
    author: "eCeez Editorial Team",
    role: "Shopify Growth Team",
    date: "2026-06-14",
